jportal_derivate_00183881/Staatshandbuch_Film_Nr_13_0018.tif p. 12]</ref>\n* {{flagcountry|Kingdom of Saxony}}: [[Order of the Rue Crown|Knight of the Rue Crown]], ''1844''<ref>{{cite book|title=Staatshandbuch f\u00fcr den Freistaat Sachsen: 1865/66|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=SBFTAAAAcAAJ&pg=PA4|year=1866|publisher=Heinrich|page=4}}</ref>\n* {{Flagcountry|Kingdom of Serbia}}: [[Order of the Cross of Takovo|Grand Cross of the Cross of Takovo]]\n* {{Flagicon image|Flag of Siam (1855).svg}} [[Siam]]:\n** Knight of the [[Order of the Royal House of Chakri]], ''9 September 1897''<ref>{{cite journal |author=[[Royal Thai Government Gazette]] |date=14 May 1899 |url=http://www.ratchakitcha.soc.go.th/DATA/PDF/2442/007/89_4.PDF |title=\u0e1e\u0e23\u0e30\u0e23\u0e32\u0e0a\u0e17\u0e32\u0e19\u0e40\u0e04\u0e23\u0e37\u0e48\u0e2d\u0e07\u0e23\u0e32\u0e0a\u0e2d\u0e34\u0e2a\u0e23\u0e34\u0e22\u0e32\u0e20\u0e23\u0e13\u0e4c\u0e17\u0e35\u0e48\u0e1b\u0e23\u0e30\u0e40\u0e17\u0e28\u0e22\u0e38\u0e42\u0e23\u0e1b (\u0e15\u0e48\u0e2d\u0e41\u0e1c\u0e48\u0e19\u0e17\u0e35\u0e48 \u0e56 \u0e2b\u0e19\u0e49\u0e32 \u0e58\u0e53)|language=Thai |access-date=2019-05-08 }}</ref>\n** [[Order of the White Elephant|Grand Cross of the White Elephant]]\n* {{Flag|Spain|1785}}: Grand Cross of the [[Order of Charles III]], ''6 April 1863''<ref>{{cite publication|url=http://hemerotecadigital.bne.es/issue.vm?id=0000941464&search=&lang=es|chapter=Real y distinguida orden de Carlos III|title=Gu\u00eda Oficial de Espa\u00f1a|last=|first=|date=1887|journal=|accessdate=21 March 2019|page=153|doi=|pmid=|language=es}}</ref>\n* {{flagicon|Sweden|1844}} {{flagicon|Norway|1844}} [[Sweden-Norway]]:\n** [[Royal Order of the Seraphim|Knight of the Seraphim]], ''17 May 1852''<ref>{{cite book|title=Sveriges och Norges statskalender|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=9JhaAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA468|year=1874|publisher=Liberf\u00f6rlag|page=468}}</ref>\n** [[Royal Norwegian Order of St. Olav|Grand Cross of St. Olav]], ''13 July 189